    {
      "num": 3,
      "geez": "ወሶበ፡ ሰምዐ፡ ማቱሳላ፡ ነገረ፡ አቡሁ፡ ሄኖክ፡ እስመ፡ በኅቡእ፡ አርአዮ፡ ኵሎ፡ ግብረ፡ ወገብአ፡ ርኢዮ፡ ወሰመዮ፡ ስሞ፡ ለዝኩ፡ ወልድ፡ ኖኅ፡ እስመ፡ ውእቱ፡ ያስተፌሥሓ፡ ለምድር፡ እምኵሉ፡ ሀጕል።",
      "translation": "And when Methuselah had heard the words of his father Enoch—for he had shown to him everything in secret—he returned and showed (them) to him and called the name of that son Noah; for he will comfort the earth after all the destruction.",
